title: Washington Department of Transportation, Major Shorelines, Washington, 1995
name: Washington Department of Transportation, Major Shorelines, Washington, 1995
description:
Abstract: Major hydrography for Washington State represented as polygons. Features in this data set define the land extent of Washington state.
Purpose: This data set is for general-purpose base maps at 1:500,000 or smaller, where detailed river information is not needed.

author.source: GIS Implementation Team, Washington State Department of Transportation
